# Composto

## Reads — composto-cachebro MCP

Use `composto-cachebro` `read_file` (not built-in Read, not bare `composto_ir`).

LOD zoom via `layer`: L0 outline → L1 default → L3 exact source.

Re-read unchanged → token-saving shortcut. After edit → IR diff.

Multi-file trace: `composto_context`. Before edits: `composto_blastradius`.
